item.title: Vandra JMS
item.description: Current Progress: A web and desktop app that supports interactive kanban boards for job applications and communications, extensive database of recruiters, cold-email generator and resume and cover letter builders. Chrome extensions with application workflows for LinkedIn and Glassdoor to automaticall add job application information to your kanban board Supported by funding source FastTrack Accelerator launched by LaunchBox Happy Valley. Working with advisors to expand on the product Demo Desktop Version: https://www.
